<br>
Bring 40-50 of them if you are just casting symbol, if you plan on doing rune double that.<br>
<br>
If you are casting Levitate type spells they normally (some exceptions here) require batwings.  <br>
<br>
It is never a bad idea to bring coffins, though luckily I never had need to use one.<br>
<br>
Most of the other components people are going to bring on their own (bone chips for necros, etc). <p>Farrnusno <BR>
